operating income in 2002 included non-recurring charges of $202 million related
to the restructuring plan (recorded in corporate and unallocated). depreciation
and amortization of $954 million included accelerated depreciation (shortened
lives) of $47 million related to the restructuring (recorded in corporate and
unallocated).
